We comply with the Children
'
s Online Privacy Protection Act (COPPA) and other applicable laws concerning the collection of information from children. Our game is intended for general audiences and is not directed at children under the age of 13. We do not knowingly collect or solicit personal information from children under 13. And we do not knowingly use personal information from children under 13. If we learn that we have collected personal information from a child under 13 without verified parental consent, we will take reasonable steps to delete such information promptly.
